name: Brewedforce
body:
### Brewing Beer just got easier..

### ..with your help!
Brewed Force is completely Open Source, so please help us build it!


### Specifications
Brewed force is an AngularJS/jQuery crossover HTML5 web application using a forked version of [BrauhausJS](https://github.com/Metgezel/brauhausjs)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
